OL,4,CExam 'anti-cheating' hats go viral in
OL,5,CPhilippines
OL,6, Images of students wearing so-called
OL,7, "anti-cheating hats" during college
OL,8, exams have gone viral on social media
OL,9, in the Philippines, sparking amusement.
OL,11,FStudents at one college in Legazpi City
OL,12,Fwere asked to wear headgear that would
OL,13,Fprevent them peeking at others' papers.
OL,15,FMany responded by creating homemade
OL,16,Fcontraptions out of cardboard, egg
OL,17,Fboxes and other recycled materials.
OL,19,FTheir tutor told the BBC she had been
OL,20,Flooking for a "fun way" to ensure
OL,21,F"integrity and honesty" in her classes.
